you gots to punish him.
Punish him hard.

37:06.308 --> 37:07.725
Day two.

37:09.644 --> 37:10.936
What you all think?

37:11.855 --> 37:13.063
ALL:
Mmm...

37:13.231 --> 37:14.273
Prommy.

37:14.482 --> 37:16.859
Yeah, too prommy.
No, too prommy.

37:17.110 --> 37:18.777
Hated it.
Yeah.

37:19.946 --> 37:23.157
All right, okay. What we thinking?

37:24.492 --> 37:25.492
Better.

37:25.660 --> 37:28.287
You need something
with a little green.

37:28.788 --> 37:30.497
Like a money-green.

37:30.790 --> 37:32.583
And spandex.
Karen.

37:33.168 --> 37:35.669
She know I'm playing with her.
Stop it.

37:35.879 --> 37:39.506
All right. What about this one?
Better.

37:39.716 --> 37:42.176
What? Now, see, this is a size 12.

37:42.385 --> 37:46.972
Why did you bring me
in this skinny-ass store?

37:47.182 --> 37:50.643
SHANTÉ: What you gonna do?
Bow! You see that there?

37:50.852 --> 37:54.521
I'll sew them together,
and pack all this up in there.

37:54.731 --> 37:57.024
This the front, this the back.

37:57.233 --> 37:58.317
SHANTÉ:
Work it.

37:58.526 --> 38:00.903
I'm big, beautiful and loving it.

38:01.821 --> 38:07.034
Day two and three for you
are a breeze. For him, it's hell.

38:07.202 --> 38:09.453
[SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY]

38:09.621 --> 38:12.665
[♪♪♪]

38:15.377 --> 38:17.836
TONY:
Keith! Are you watching the game?

38:23.051 --> 38:26.053
MAN [ON TV]:
I'm hearing, and what God says is,

38:26.221 --> 38:28.389
"When I show you the truth..."

38:28.556 --> 38:34.728
If I stay out late Saturday, I attend
church via TV Sunday morning.
I keep up with my religion.

38:34.896 --> 38:36.021
[PHONE RINGING]

38:36.189 --> 38:39.650
SHANTÉ [ON RECORDING]:
What up? This is Shanté.
At the beep, do your thing.

38:39.818 --> 38:40.818
[BEEPS]

38:40.986 --> 38:43.570
KEITH:
This is Keith.
I called you yesterday.

38:43.738 --> 38:47.241
You didn't return my call.
If you're there, pick up.

38:47.575 --> 38:50.035
If you're there, pick up.

38:50.870 --> 38:53.038
Cool. Call me when you get in.

38:53.373 --> 38:56.250
In love and war,
maintain military silence.

38:56.459 --> 38:59.670
Don't speak or consort with
the enemy. Silence is golden.

38:59.838 --> 39:00.963
[PHONE RINGING]

39:01.131 --> 39:03.215
You can do more with silence
than speaking.

39:03.425 --> 39:06.885
What up? This is Shanté.
At the beep, do your thing.

39:07.053 --> 39:08.053
[BEEPS]

39:08.221 --> 39:11.724
KEITH:
I'm picking up some tickets
to the Lauryn Hill concert.

39:11.933 --> 39:14.476
So just let me know
if you wanna go.

39:14.728 --> 39:19.106
See? He think he's slick.
You know I love Lauryn Hill.

39:19.774 --> 39:22.484
That's okay.
I'm going to church anyway.

39:22.736 --> 39:26.739
Like Mama said, better to get
there late than not at all.

39:26.948 --> 39:29.950
Lauryn Hill. No, you didn't.

39:32.954 --> 39:37.166
No, I can't call. I'm not gonna call.
Called twice already.

39:37.417 --> 39:38.959
Can't be desperate.

39:39.377 --> 39:41.754
Okay. Oh, no.

39:42.255 --> 39:44.298
Okay, all right. No.

39:44.716 --> 39:48.385
[CHOIR SINGING
"STANDING IN THE NEED"]

40:02.776 --> 40:04.902
[SINGING
"STANDING IN THE NEED"]

40:10.867 --> 40:12.326
[GRUNTING]

41:00.458 --> 41:02.835
[DOORBELL RINGS]

41:03.002 --> 41:04.878
[POUNDING ON DOOR]

41:13.388 --> 41:15.430
Aww. It's you, man.

41:15.640 --> 41:20.894
Who else are you expecting, dog?
Come on, you're not even ready.

41:21.062 --> 41:26.108
I forgot I had these briefs
to prepare, so I can't make it today.

41:26.901 --> 41:30.070
You're not thinking about Shanté?
Come on, man. No, man.

41:30.363 --> 41:33.407
Keith.
I'm not thinking about that girl.

41:34.784 --> 41:37.244
All right. I see you later, man.

41:37.453 --> 41:39.955
Tell them I'm sorry
I couldn't make it.

41:40.165 --> 41:42.708
I'm about to be Tiger Woods.

41:43.626 --> 41:45.586
SHANTÉ:
He's still playing it cool.

41:45.962 --> 41:49.381
He's upset,
but he has things under control.

41:49.591 --> 41:51.675
His ego won't let him go far.

41:51.885 --> 41:55.554
So, what do you do?
You break him. Push his buttons.

41:55.763 --> 41:58.807
To do this, you need a PR agent
and a flunky.

41:59.017 --> 42:01.810
Okay, who's the PR agent,
and who's the flunky?

42:01.978 --> 42:03.187
Hey, sister, how you...?

42:03.479 --> 42:06.273
Hey, Trent.
Shanté.

42:06.482 --> 42:08.317
How you doing?
Good.

42:08.526 --> 42:11.445
Oh, my brother. My brother.

42:11.654 --> 42:14.031
Good to see you.
What's all this?

42:14.240 --> 42:16.950
Your PR agent should be
watching you.

42:17.160 --> 42:20.120
He must be a friend of your man's.

42:20.288 --> 42:25.167
Don't do anything sleazy.
Just be a little too friendly.

42:25.376 --> 42:28.795
You do this by holding your
flunky too long

42:28.963 --> 42:31.048
and hugging him too tight.

42:31.257 --> 42:33.967
Damn! That sure was
one hell of a hug.

42:34.135 --> 42:36.803
I'm just happy to see
a Christian brother.

42:36.971 --> 42:40.641
It's good to see you.
I can't wait to holler out.

42:40.892 --> 42:41.934
Have a blessed week.

42:42.101 --> 42:43.518
I sure will.
My brother.

42:43.728 --> 42:45.312
Bless on, baby.
Bless.

42:45.563 --> 42:49.983
Contrary to popular belief,
men are big gossipers too.

42:50.151 --> 42:54.488
They love to talk about something
they done seen or know.

42:54.739 --> 42:57.324
You won't believe what
we saw at church.

42:57.575 --> 42:58.742
What y'all see?

42:58.952 --> 43:01.078
Trent and Shanté was
all hugged up.

43:02.914 --> 43:05.165
Keith's Shanté?
Hell, yeah.

43:05.416 --> 43:08.961
What are you talking about?
I know what I saw.

43:09.170 --> 43:12.965
They was basically grinding up
in the lobby. Tight.

43:13.174 --> 43:14.800
That was just a Christian hug.

43:15.009 --> 43:20.097
Sometime she just feels the spirit,
and she wanna spread the word.

43:20.306 --> 43:24.476
"Christian hug," my ass.
I know what a Christian hug is.

43:24.686 --> 43:28.438
When girls give you a little hug
with their asses out

43:28.648 --> 43:32.859
so you got that space in case
you get a little excited.

43:33.027 --> 43:37.114
You don't want them to feel
your man-man in church.

43:37.323 --> 43:40.617
But there was no gap.
They was hugged up tight.

43:40.827 --> 43:44.037
Why she hugged up on him
like that anyway

43:44.205 --> 43:46.290
knowing he's the major player?

43:46.499 --> 43:51.420
Trent's a player? He go to church.
All the players go to church.

43:51.671 --> 43:54.881
Why? Because all the freaks
go to church.

43:55.091 --> 43:58.218
I ain't lying. Patrick, am I lying?
Am I lying?

43:58.386 --> 44:02.889
Go to a club Saturday night.
Go to church Sunday morning.

44:03.099 --> 44:07.894
I guarantee you the same ho's
you see on the dance floor,

44:08.104 --> 44:10.105
you see Sunday morning
singing in the choir.

44:10.273 --> 44:11.523
[SINGS]

44:11.691 --> 44:14.693
That's real.
You got the deaconess,

44:14.902 --> 44:17.446
you got the usher board.
Please!

44:17.697 --> 44:20.574
Why wouldn't a player
hang out in church?

44:21.034 --> 44:24.703
Club on Saturday,
how much is it to get in?

44:24.912 --> 44:27.080
Fifteen dollars.
Fifteen dollars.

44:27.290 --> 44:29.541
You go to church Sunday,
how much?

44:30.376 --> 44:31.793
Nigga, that shit is free!

44:33.463 --> 44:37.632
Trust me, bro. A whole gang
of players be going to church.

44:38.217 --> 44:40.802
You might be right.
I'm right.

44:41.554 --> 44:44.931
Tell you right now,
Trent fixing to wax that ass.

44:45.558 --> 44:50.103
When you're gossiped about,
there's always backlash involved.

44:50.313 --> 44:52.356
But trust me,
the tradeoff is worth it.

44:52.523 --> 44:54.191
[CAMEO'S "SHAKE YOUR PANTS"
PLAYING]

44:54.359 --> 44:56.860
Shanté, pick up. It's Keith.
Give me a call, okay?

44:57.070 --> 45:00.322
You're still not in,
so just give me a call.

45:00.698 --> 45:02.282
It's me again.

45:02.492 --> 45:06.745
I've called you eight times.
I don't know where you are.

45:06.954 --> 45:12.125
Where you at? Where you be?
What's up? It's me again. It's 6:00.

45:12.335 --> 45:16.380
Yeah, yeah, 6:00.
Just waiting for your call.

45:16.589 --> 45:20.467
I know you're not still in church,
so give me a call.

45:20.676 --> 45:22.260
Yeah, yeah, it's 6:00.

45:22.470 --> 45:26.139
This is the last time
I'm calling your ass. Peace.

45:26.307 --> 45:28.767
What does she think
this is? Please.

45:28.976 --> 45:31.103
Okay, I decided to call you back.

45:31.979 --> 45:35.774
Don't know where you are.
Just call me, all right?

45:36.818 --> 45:38.652
KEITH [ON MESSAGE]:
Shanté, it's 11:00.

45:38.820 --> 45:40.153
[♪♪♪]

45:40.321 --> 45:41.947
All right. Bye-bye.

45:42.657 --> 45:44.533
It's called tough love.

45:44.826 --> 45:46.326
Day four.

45:48.788 --> 45:51.331
The buying power
of African-Americans

45:51.499 --> 45:53.333
is up 12 percent in groceries.

45:53.501 --> 45:58.839
It's tapering off in alcohol largely
due to special interest groups.

45:59.006 --> 46:02.592
I think we can improve
if we limit our marketing

46:02.802 --> 46:05.512
and focus on
after-school projects,

46:05.763 --> 46:08.014
thereby helping the community.

46:08.266 --> 46:11.852
People will see us still targeting
African-Americans

46:12.019 --> 46:14.521
and providing
a community service.

46:14.772 --> 46:18.567
So we're redirecting our energies.
Exactly, Bill.

46:18.776 --> 46:22.446
We're turning it into
a positive relationship.

46:22.655 --> 46:24.322
That's very good.
Thanks.

46:24.532 --> 46:25.657
Well done.

46:26.534 --> 46:29.536
Look at these people.
Notice anything different?

46:29.745 --> 46:32.038
Moi. I'm 28 years old,

46:32.248 --> 46:35.292
a sister and still made partner.

46:35.751 --> 46:38.712
Keith should be calling
any second now.

46:38.880 --> 46:41.298
[PHONE RINGING]

46:41.466 --> 46:43.675
Hello?
Keith is on line two.

46:43.885 --> 46:45.552
Good. Tell him I'm busy.

46:45.720 --> 46:49.723
You've been waiting for his call.
Tell him I'm busy.

46:52.059 --> 46:55.145
Women.
I'm a stinker, ain't I?

46:56.063 --> 46:58.815
I'm sorry. Mr. Fenton,
she's still busy.

46:59.066 --> 47:01.401
[CAMEO'S "SHAKE YOUR PANTS"
PLAYING]

47:06.240 --> 47:09.242
TONY:
Come on, Keith!
I know you're in there, man.

47:10.745 --> 47:11.953
Keith!

47:12.163 --> 47:15.749
I know you can see me,
because I can see you!

47:17.168 --> 47:19.920
Come on, man.
Don't give me that look.

47:20.129 --> 47:22.589
Look into the light, Keith!

47:22.840 --> 47:25.675
Look into the light!
I'm coming around!

47:26.844 --> 47:29.054
I must admit I feel sorry for Keith.

47:29.263 --> 47:32.307
I hate to see people suffer.
But you know what?

47:32.517 --> 47:36.228
You can't show weakness.
Men only understand strength.

47:36.437 --> 47:41.399
If they don't feel pain,
there'll be no gain.
No pain, no gain.

47:41.567 --> 47:42.609
[♪♪♪]

47:42.777 --> 47:47.364
What the hell is wrong with you?
You ain't come to work today.

47:47.615 --> 47:50.075
Don't look like
you washed your ass.

47:50.284 --> 47:53.203
Keith, what's wrong?
No, man. I'm...

47:54.622 --> 47:56.039
I think I'm sick.

47:56.249 --> 48:00.335
You ain't sick, man.
No, man. I mean, I'm sick, bro.

48:00.628 --> 48:03.797
You wanna feel my head?
I think I got the flu.

48:04.006 --> 48:05.632
You ain't got
no damn flu.

48:05.841 --> 48:09.302
No, I got... I'm telling you.
I feel woozy.

48:09.512 --> 48:10.845
Woozy?

48:11.138 --> 48:13.139
No, dog. You whipped.

48:13.349 --> 48:15.976
She got you laid out
like a $2 crack ho.

48:16.185 --> 48:19.813
You look like you waiting on a hit.
It's sad, bro.

48:20.106 --> 48:21.648
This sad.

48:23.025 --> 48:24.276
Look at you.

48:25.903 --> 48:27.737
I'll go call your mama.

48:28.698 --> 48:32.284
They'll take your player card
for this. I'll see to it.

48:34.161 --> 48:35.996
COMPUTERIZED VOICE:
You have 11 messages.

48:36.205 --> 48:38.623
That's what I'm talking about.

48:40.084 --> 48:44.629
By this time, he gets advice
from his boys, which can get sticky.

48:44.839 --> 48:47.507
So whatever you do,
don't talk to him.

48:47.717 --> 48:51.886
Phone, two-way, pager.
Nothing, nada.

48:52.388 --> 48:57.309
But be careful, he might pull
a fast one on you and just come over.

48:57.518 --> 48:59.769
And then you're in trouble.

48:59.937 --> 49:02.397
[DOORBELL RINGS]

49:10.990 --> 49:12.032
Keith.

49:12.199 --> 49:15.493
[CAMEO'S "SHAKE YOUR PANTS"
PLAYING]

49:18.664 --> 49:22.000
What's going on?
Doing all right? Okay.

49:22.293 --> 49:24.919
I heard you were sick.
You know better.

49:32.803 --> 49:36.222
TONY: How you feeling?
I'm feeling real good right now.

49:36.432 --> 49:38.516
Did you do what I said?
Relax.

49:38.726 --> 49:42.395
Did you do what I said?
Have a seat. I'll break it down.

49:42.605 --> 49:46.024
I won't until you tell me
if you did what I told you.

49:46.233 --> 49:49.235
I did exactly what you said.

49:49.779 --> 49:52.030
Exactly what you told me.
Damn.

49:52.239 --> 49:54.574
I got over there about 10:00,

49:54.784 --> 49:58.828
all dressed up,
looking good and suave

49:59.789 --> 50:01.081
and debonair.

50:01.290 --> 50:04.542
Like Denzel?
Better than Denzel.

50:04.752 --> 50:06.920
Shit, let me sit down then.

50:07.129 --> 50:08.213
Come in.

50:08.798 --> 50:11.132
KEITH:
So she invited me in.

50:11.342 --> 50:14.969
Walked in there all calm,
cool and collected.

50:15.137 --> 50:18.056
[JODECI'S "STAY" PLAYING]

50:18.224 --> 50:19.599
[QUIETLY]
Uh-oh.

50:19.767 --> 50:24.813
Started to dim the lights all over.
Got some soft music playing.

50:25.022 --> 50:27.107
She knew I was there
to make a move.

50:27.316 --> 50:30.276
Sat down on the couch,
looking all good

50:30.486 --> 50:32.904
like chocolate Häagen-Dazs
ice cream.

50:33.114 --> 50:35.407
With the nuts.
With the nuts.

50:35.616 --> 50:38.493
Looking all luscious and lickety.

50:39.328 --> 50:41.121
I was there to seduce.

50:41.330 --> 50:44.165
Gave her that Denzel eye thing,

50:44.417 --> 50:47.127
then a little L.L. Lip action.

50:47.336 --> 50:50.422
It was about to be on.
TONY: So did you hit?

50:50.631 --> 50:53.216
Relax, relax.
No, did you hit?

50:53.426 --> 50:57.137
Relax, all right?
Come on. You hit it, right?

50:59.765 --> 51:02.600
KEITH: Started moving in for the kill.
TONY: And then?

51:02.810 --> 51:06.146
KEITH: She too smart for that.
Told you that.

51:06.355 --> 51:09.482
But plan B.

51:10.651 --> 51:12.402
So you had plan B?

51:12.611 --> 51:15.655
KEITH:
Started an argument.
Didn't matter about what.

51:15.865 --> 51:17.782
I got her yelling at me.

51:17.992 --> 51:22.537
I drew her into me emotionally.
After it was over, I just...

51:22.788 --> 51:26.291
I felt so good, like jogging.
TONY: See, that's it.

51:26.500 --> 51:29.919
The transference of frustration
from one party to the next.

51:30.129 --> 51:32.505
You right about that.
Of course.

51:32.715 --> 51:34.382
You take physics?
Oh, yeah.

51:34.633 --> 51:38.178
What's the law of thermodynamic
energy by Newton?

51:38.637 --> 51:41.514
Energy is neither lost nor destroyed.
I remember.

51:41.724 --> 51:44.559
It is transferred from one party
to the next.

51:44.810 --> 51:46.436
Right.
We all experience it.

51:46.645 --> 51:49.147
Feeling good?
Feeling real good now.

51:49.356 --> 51:51.733
Somebody full of negative energy

51:51.984 --> 51:54.611
leaves you feeling
completely drained.

51:54.820 --> 51:57.489
Sucks it out of you.
Transference of energy.

51:57.698 --> 51:59.282
That's what you did.

51:59.492 --> 52:03.828
You transferred your negative energy
and emotions onto her.

52:04.371 --> 52:06.289
You flipped the script.

52:06.499 --> 52:09.375
Was I flipping it?
You flipped it.

52:09.668 --> 52:12.545
Women, they emotional creatures.
Preach.

52:12.755 --> 52:16.800
Once you tap into their emotions,
you're halfway there.

52:16.967 --> 52:19.427
Testify!
It doesn't matter what type of emotion.

52:19.595 --> 52:20.845
[HYMN PLAYING]

52:21.013 --> 52:22.180
I'll beat a drum.

52:22.389 --> 52:25.558
Once those emotional floodgates
are open,

52:25.726 --> 52:27.727
you're home free.
Home free!

52:27.937 --> 52:29.729
They get confused.
Confused.

52:29.939 --> 52:31.731
Bewildered.
Bewildered!

52:31.941 --> 52:33.525
Lethargic.
Lethargic!

52:33.692 --> 52:35.652
Whoo!
Amen, amen!

52:35.861 --> 52:37.529
Amen, baby!
Yeah, amen!

52:37.738 --> 52:40.532
Hallelujah! Hallelujah!
Whoo!

52:43.077 --> 52:46.704
Will somebody please
cut that damn music?

52:46.872 --> 52:48.998
[HYMN STOPS]

52:51.210 --> 52:55.171
Day five is a bad day.
That's all I gotta say.

52:55.840 --> 52:57.924
[♪♪♪]

53:00.719 --> 53:02.637
[SIGHS]

53:02.805 --> 53:07.058
Day six is a bad day,
but not as bad as five.

53:07.560 --> 53:12.272
So he turned the tables on you
with the transfer-of-emotion shit.

53:12.439 --> 53:15.441
I ain't gonna lie.
That shit does work.

53:15.609 --> 53:18.862
So now you got to turn
the tables back on him.

53:19.071 --> 53:23.408
But until you do that,
what must you do? Hm?

53:23.576 --> 53:27.745
Occupy your damn time.
Stay busy.

53:28.163 --> 53:30.081
Y'all know what I mean.

53:30.291 --> 53:34.752
So in times like these,
this is what I do, ladies.

53:35.671 --> 53:38.339
I break out the old black book.

53:39.174 --> 53:41.551
While you're thinking about him,

53:41.760 --> 53:46.097
he's having a good time
not thinking about you.

53:46.974 --> 53:48.600
Tyrone.

53:48.809 --> 53:50.435
Call Tyrone.

53:50.603 --> 53:55.106
[MELKY SEDECK'S
"KITTY KAT WORLD"
PLAYING OVER SPEAKERS]

53:55.274 --> 53:58.234
Come down low.
Put it in my face.

53:58.444 --> 54:01.279
I want it to be funky.
Ow! Ooh!

54:01.447 --> 54:04.782
How you doing?
You were right, man.

54:05.284 --> 54:08.161
I feel like my old self again.
Told you.

54:10.372 --> 54:13.583
You didn't know a big man
could move like this.

54:14.835 --> 54:16.753
CONNY: How do you like that?
Whoa, whoa!

54:16.921 --> 54:18.338
What's going on?

54:19.131 --> 54:20.840
Spin it around on me, baby.

54:21.133 --> 54:23.968
Spin it. Whoo! You my own
little spinning top.

54:25.262 --> 54:29.933
Hey, whoa. What's going on?
I'm enjoying myself.

54:30.142 --> 54:32.685
I see you.
You see me?

54:32.895 --> 54:36.147
What's going on down there?
Turn around.

54:37.191 --> 54:39.901
I'm glad you made it
to my promotion.

54:40.152 --> 54:42.570
It's nice to mix
business with pleasure.

54:42.738 --> 54:45.031
Hey! That's the nipple.
I know.

54:45.741 --> 54:47.700
Business with pleasure.

54:47.910 --> 54:51.329
